# SIEM Alert Investigation & Incident Response Project

## 📌 Overview
This project demonstrates my ability to analyze security alerts and respond to potential threats using Security Information and Event Management (SIEM) concepts. The goal was to investigate a simulated security alert, determine its validity, and follow an incident response playbook to contain and resolve the issue.

---

## 🚨 Scenario
A SIEM system generated an alert indicating a suspicious file download on a network endpoint. I was tasked with investigating the alert and determining whether it represented a legitimate security threat.

---

